            "text": "<h2><br/>Statement & Uniqueness on Red Carpets</h2><p>Celebrities wearing his sarees are making statements: whether it’s a bridal outfit or a special event like the Met Gala, these sarees stand out because of custom design, precious details, and dramatic silhouettes. For example, one high-profile celebrity wore a custom Sabyasachi saree with gemstones, intricate embroidery, and a long train, made by many artisans over many hours.</p><p>Because of that attention to detail and evocative design, the sarees become instantly iconic — <a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/fashion/content/from-alia-bhatt-to-karisma-kapoor-this-is-the-celebrity-way-to-style-a-sabyasachi-sari?utm_source=chatgpt.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">something the celebrities can be celebrated for</span></a>.<br/><br/></p>",
