            "text_size": "40,15",
            "txt_align": "start",
            "sub_heading": "",
            "heading": "",
            "text": "<h2>Emotion, Status & Bridal Allure</h2><p>Sabyasachi is widely regarded in the bridal space. Many high-profile weddings have chosen his sarees or bridal ensembles. That gives the saree not only aesthetic value but also emotional significance. Celebs choose his work because it signals heritage, elegance, and exclusivity.</p><p>Wearing his saree becomes part of a narrative: tradition, legacy, craftsmanship, and status. That makes it a powerful piece for public events, weddings, or special occasions.</p>",
